tags.FIXME:1: There is a small sidepath between Schlederloh and river Loisach, which is only one way (175097282) and is closed to protect nature (see note at way). Can this way be removed?
tags.FIXME:2: In bing the roundabout in Belluno (Viale Europa) does not look like to be a good place for walking/crossing the streets. But first better mapping of roundabout itself is needed, before route can be improved.
tags.FIXME:3: There is a longer dead end in southern Belluno (along Via Dino Buzzati), which might probably have been an alternate route, but now is cut of (as of 2018-08-30). It has been moved to the end of the relation. Can this be removed?

tags.note:1: In the valley south of Wattens and Wattenberg there are two alternate ways: Alternative 1 (more track like according to bing);Alternative 2 (more path like according to bing).
tags.note:2: Relation is ordered: "Mainroute north"+ Alternative 1;Alternative 2 + MainRoute south;having an interrupt between Alternative 1 and Alternative 2
tags.note:3: There is an alternate route near Rocca Pietore/Pezze. Relation is orddered: MainRoute from West+Alternate 1;Gap;Alternate 2+MainRoute to East.
tags.note:4: There is a small alternative (single way) near Masare. Relation is ordered: Main from NW+Alternate 1;Gap;Alternate 2 + Main to SW
tags.note:5: There is an alternate between Weitental/Vallarga and Lahner. Relation is sorted: MainRoute from north+Alternative 1;Gap;Alternative 2+MainRoute to south
tags.note:6: There is an alternative around Pfunders/Fundres. Relation is sorted: MainRoute from north+alternate 1;gap;Alternate 2+MainRoute to south
